<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">The Fifth Conference on Innovative Applications of Artificial Intelligence</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p><p><b>Edited by Philip Klahr and Elizabeth Byrnes</b></p><p>July 11&ndash;15, 1993, Washington, D.C. Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/iaai93.php">This proceedings is also available in book and CD format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text may be restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><h3 class="left">Contents</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/Papers/IAAI93-018.pdf" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Preface</a> / v</p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/Papers/IAAI93-019.pdf" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">IAAI Organization</a> / v</p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Quality and Knowledge in Software Engineering</a> / 3<br /><i>Stu Burton, Celite Corporation; Kent Swanson and Lisa Leonard, Andersen Consulting</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Computer Aided Parts Estimation </a> / 16<br /><i>Adam Cunningham, Ford Motor Company; and Robert Smart, Inference Europe, Inc.</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">ESDS: Materials Technology Knowledge Bases Supporting Design of Boeing Jetliners</a> / 26<br /><i>Mark A. Dahl, The Boeing Company</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">PI-in-a-Box: A Knowledge-Based System for Space Science Experimentation</a> / 34<br /><i>Richard Frainier and Nicolas Groleau, RECOM Technologies, Inc.; Lyman Hazelton, Peter Szolovits and Laurence Young, Massachusetts Institute of Technology; Silvano Colombano and Irving Statler, NASA Ames Research Center; Michael Compton, Sterling Software</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Digitized Expert PICTures (DEPICT): An Intelligent Information Repository</a> / 50<br /><i>George Gallant and Janet Thygesen, IBM Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">GCESS: A Symptom Driven Diagnostic Shell and Related Applications</a> / 61<br /><i>Peter Holtzman, Inference Corporation and Ray Fischer, Northrop Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Pitch Expert: A Problem-Solving System for Kraft Mills </a> / 75<br /><i>A. Kowalski, CRIM; D. Bouchard, L. H. Allen, Y. Larin and O. Vadas, Paprican</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">OPERA: A Highly Interactive Expert System for Outside Plant Engineering </a> / 95<br /><i>Gary Lazarus, Lien Tran and Marty Baade, NYNEX Science &amp; Technology</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Dodger, a Diagnostic Expert System for the Evaluation of Nondestructive Test Data</a> / 107<br /><i>Arthur J. Levy, Jane E. Oppenlander, David M. Brudnoy, James M. Englund, Kent C. Loomis and Arnold M. Barsky, General Electric Company</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Expanding the Utility of Legacy Systems </a> / 118<br /><i>Joseph McManus, AT&amp;T Network Systems and Teresa Garland, Inference Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Managing Product Quality By Integrating Operations Research and Artificial Intelligence Technologies</a> / 126<br /><i>Charles S. Moon, Thomas M. Moore and Suheil M. Nasser, IBM Industrial Sector Consulting Services</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">COMPAQ QuickSource: Providing the Consumer with the Power of Artificial Intelligence</a> / 142<br /><i>Trung Nguyen and Mary Czerwinsksi, Compaq Computer Corporation and Dan Lee, Inference Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Diagnostic Yield Characterization Expert (DYCE)--A Diagnostic Knowledge Based System Shell for Automated Data Analysis / 152</a> <br /><i>Donald D. Pierson and George J. Gallant, IBM Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Tennessee Offender Management Information System</a> / 161<br /><i>David Reynolds, Andersen Consulting and Tim Beck, Tennessee Department of Correction</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The DRAIR Advisor: A Knowledge-Based System for Materiel Deficiency Analysis</a> / 169<br /><i>Brian L. Robey, Pamela K. Fink, Sanjeev Venkatesan and Carol L. Redfield, Southwest Research Institute; Jerry W. Ferguson, US Air Force Materiel Command</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1993/iaai93-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Knowledge-Based Configurator that Supports Sales, Engineering, and Manufacturing at AT&amp;/T Network Systems</a> / 183<br /><i>Jon R. Wright, Elia S. Weixelbaum, Karen E. Brown, Gregg T. Vesonder, Stephen R. Palmer, Jay I. Berman and Harry H. Moore, AT&amp;T Bell Laboratories</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/Papers/IAAI93-017.pdf" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Index</a></p> </div></div></div><div id="left">
